<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="page-container">
  <div class="page-header" data-animate="slide-up">
    <h1>Returns & Refunds</h1>
    <p>Our commitment to your satisfaction doesn't end at checkout. We've made our return process as simple as possible.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="prose" data-animate="fade-in">
    <h2>30-Day Return Policy</h2>
    <p>If you are not completely satisfied with your purchase, you may return it within 30 days of delivery for a full refund or exchange. Items must be in their original condition and packaging with all tags attached.</p>

    <h2>How to Initiate a Return</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Log into your account and navigate to "My Orders".</li>
      <li>Select the order containing the item you wish to return.</li>
      <li>Click "Return Item" and follow the prompts to generate a prepaid return shipping label.</li>
      <li>Pack the item securely and attach the label to the outside of the box.</li>
      <li>Drop the package off at any authorized carrier location.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Refund Processing Time</h2>
    <p>Once we receive your return, please allow 3-5 business days for our warehouse to inspect the item. After inspection, we will initiate a refund to your original payment method. Depending on your bank, it may take an additional 2-7 business days for the funds to appear in your account.</p>

    <h2>Non-Returnable Items</h2>
    <p>Certain items cannot be returned due to hygiene or safety reasons. These include intimate apparel, personalized items, and perishable goods. Final sale items are also non-returnable.</p>
  </div>
</div>

